Version 1.0.2
=============

* Added result file creation, with switch (-o) to bypass this behavior.
* Added display of resulting filename name and its hash (SHA256)..
* Added passcode facility (see next).
* Added shift values (min & max) altering technique.
	- calculate digit sum from file's size.
	- calculate digit sum from passcode character values.
	- add both digit sums.
	- subtract this sum from the shift minimum value and add that sum to the shift maximum value.
